task.summary: avtar image issue and Calendar issue resolved.
avtar image issue and Calendar issue resolved.
- Create ChildCalendar - Rename button "Show All". Change click area. Remove icon
- fix return back to Child Calendar screen bug(Not all dates displayed).
- Hidden the "Goals Line" bottom on the Child's Calendar Screen.
- fix bug "App crashing from task view"
- Add balance activity. Hide Goals from Task View Activity.
- Single instance of delete for repeat tasks and repeat tasks being limited to 7 bug.
- After approve one the screen reload no longer shows the others to approve.
- Fix a bug with a limited repetition of tasks.
Fixed bugs: 1) Child calendar failure 2) Task Approval from "Task editing screen" 3) Different dates of due tasks
Fixed bugs: 1) Monthly Calendar Repeat(days of the week) 2) Fixed application crash when BalanceActivity is opened 3) Changed headers order in the task view
1) Balance screen - bug with goals amount fixed 2) Bug with weekly tasks fixed
